---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout description="Affest Chefs Highlight" title="Chefs · Affest">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <header class="py-14 text-center sm:py-20">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
        Affest Chefs Highlight
      </h1>
    </header>

    <section class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 sm:gap-16">
      <!-- Amal -->
      <article
        class="grid grid-cols-1 items-start gap-6 border-b border-green-100 pb-10 sm:grid-cols-3"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center sm:items-start">
          <img
            class="h-80 w-auto rounded-md object-cover"
            src="/assets/chef-2.jpg"
            alt="Portrait of Amal Abdulrazaq Muhammad"
          />
          <h2
            class="mt-4 text-center text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-left sm:text-3xl"
          >
            Amal Abdulrazaq Muhammad
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="sm:col-span-2">
          <p class="text-lg leading-8 text-primary-950/70">
            Amal Abdulrazaq Muhammad is a dynamic photographer and storyteller, weaving together the
            art of imagery and the power of words. A graduate of Kaduna State University, where she
            studied mass communication, Amal finds inspiration in the world around her, capturing
            moments through her lens while penning short stories and poetry that resonate with her
            inner thoughts and emotions.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-8 text-primary-950/70">
            Her culinary passion ignited at just six years old, and by the time she was nine, she
            was exploring the kitchen independently, guided by the encouragement of family and
            friends. For Amal, the kitchen is a sanctuary—a space where she transforms her feelings
            into delicious creations and clears her mind amidst life's complexities.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-8 text-primary-950/70">
            With a unique blend of creativity in photography, writing, and cooking, Amal continues
            to express her vibrant spirit, inviting others to see the beauty in both art and
            everyday life.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Jonah -->
      <article
        class="grid grid-cols-1 items-start gap-6 border-b border-green-100 pb-10 sm:grid-cols-3"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center sm:items-start">
          <img
            class="h-80 w-auto rounded-md object-cover"
            src="/assets/team/amina.jpg"
            alt="Portrait of Jonah Yakubu"
          />
          <h2
            class="mt-4 text-center text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-left sm:text-3xl"
          >
            Amina Maiwada
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="sm:col-span-2">
          <p></p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Aisha -->
      <article
        class="grid grid-cols-1 items-start gap-6 border-b border-green-100 pb-10 sm:grid-cols-3"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center sm:items-start">
          <img
            class="h-80 w-auto rounded-md object-cover"
            src="/assets/chef-3.jpeg"
            alt="Portrait of Aisha Tilde"
          />
          <h2
            class="mt-4 text-center text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-left sm:text-3xl"
          >
            Aisha Tilde
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="sm:col-span-2">
          <p class="text-lg leading-8 text-primary-950/70">
            A chef | Student nurse | Food enthusiast. Passionate about blending culinary creativity,
            northern delicacies, and healthcare insights.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
